data.description: Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a 2-car garage, this property is perfect for those seeking comfort and convenience. Step inside and be greeted by an open-concept floor plan, with the dining room and its large windows overlooking the front yard. The beautifully designed kitchen features white stained cabinetry, granite countertops, and an oversized island. The family room is bathed in natural light, thanks to its large windows and exquisite flooring. Retreat to the primary suite, located at the rear of the home, and enjoy the view of the backyard through its generous windows. The primary bath offers a spacious walk-in shower, a separate garden tub, and a walk-in closet. The secondary bedrooms are situated in the front of the home, providing privacy and tranquility. Step outside to the covered patio and take in the beauty of the backyard. This home also comes equipped with a water softener/filter system. It was built in 2022 and is zoned to the esteemed Lamar Consolidated ISD.
